  Exchange currency
  ask if the user wants to know about the exchange rate first or convert the currency directly
  if Know about the exchange rate:
    call acquisitionRate
    tell the user of the exchange rate based on the returned exchange_rate_table
  else if Exchange currency directly:
    call exchangeMoney to exchange currency
    if success:
      Tell the user to check the currency that has been sent to his/her account
    else:
      judge which of the following is corresponding: no exchange times, exceed the foreign exchange limit, or have an insufficient balance based on the returned exchange_result
      if No exchange times:
        Explain that the number of Express Redemption times for this year has been used up
      else if Exceed the foreign exchange limit:
        Inform that the foreign exchange control limit has been exceeded
      else if Insufficient balance:
        Inform that the balance in the account is insufficient

12233102-ba1a-4302-b284-05428cc3547f.workflow:
[start] Start
    ask_diagnosis()
    if is_diagnosis_issued:
        notify_diagnosis_issued()
        if needs_medication:
            inform_medication_info()
            if wants_quick_purchase:
                attempt_quick_purchase()
            else:
                pay_at_hospital()
        elif needs_hospitalization:
            inform_hospitalization()
        else:
            inform_no_treatment_needed()
    else:
        notify_diagnosis_pending()

def ask_diagnosis():
    Ask for user information
    Call getMedical to check medical progress
    Confirm if the doctor issues a diagnosis based on the returned is_check

def notify_diagnosis_issued():
    Notify the user that the doctor has issued a diagnosis
    Confirm if the user needs medication, hospitalization, or no treatment based on the returned is_check

def inform_medication_info():
    Inform the user of medication information based on the returned purchase_medication
    Ask if the user wants to make a quick purchase
    if the user wants quick purchase:
        if user is not bound or has insufficient balance:
            request the user to bind, recharge, or not use quick purchase
        else:
            call orderMedication to order medication
            process information for the user based on the returned result_text
    else:
        Request the user to pay at the hospital charge office
        Then pick up the medicine according to the charge sheet

def inform_hospitalization():
    Inform the user of the need for hospitalization
    Ask the user to go to the front desk of the corresponding department to make a record
    Specific information will be provided by the front desk

def inform_no_treatment_needed():
    The user is diagnosed with no need for treatment
    Ask the user to relax
    Being doubtful, the user can go to a larger hospital or seek psychological consultation

def notify_diagnosis_pending():
    Notify the user that the doctor has not issued a diagnosis yet
    Ask the user to wait for a while before coming back
    If the diagnosis has not been made for a long time, ask the user to contact the doctor for another appointment

def attempt_quick_purchase():
    Quick Purchase will use the cost of the user's bound account
    If the user is not bound or has an insufficient balance:
        request the user to bind, recharge, or not use quick purchase
    Else:
        call orderMedication to order medication
        process information for the user based on the returned result_text

def pay_at_hospital():
    Request the user to pay at the hospital charge office
    Then pick up the medicine according to the charge sheet

